<p><span>[2] </span><span>陈静茹</span><span>,</span><span>孟庆佳</span><span>,</span><span>康乐</span><span>,</span><span>等</span><span>.</span><span>低血糖生成指数谷物及其制品研究进展与法规管理现状</span><span>[J].</span><span>食品工业科技</span><span>,2020,41(18):338-343.</span></p>
